{"lemma":"حُلْقُومِ","slug":"حُلْقُومِ","root":"ح.ل.ق.م","root_slug":"ح-ل-ق-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ل-ق-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حُلْقُوم","root":"حلق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8880","n8901"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8F%D9%84%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8F%D9%88%D9%85%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"throat, gullet"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"esophagus, place of the epiglottis"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"trachea, windpipe"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fauces"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ellipsis of رَاحَةُ ٱلْحُلْقُوم (rāḥatu l-ḥulqūm)","tags":["abbreviation","alt-of","ellipsis"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ح ل ق (ḥ l q) meaning \"to razor something\", hence the place or portions severed when slaughtering an animal."},"ipa":["/ħul.quːm/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8880","headword_ar":"حُلْقُومٌ","root":"Hlq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqN","text_ar":"حَلْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n8901","headword_ar":"حُلْقُومٌ","root":"Hlqm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"windpipe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passage of the breath;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, Mgh, TA;) by the cutting, or severing, of which, and of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mariYo'","text_ar":"مَرِىْء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or œsophagus] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wadajaAni","text_ar":"وَدَجَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or two external jugular veins], the lawful slaughtering of an animal is completed: (T, TA:) accord. to the S and K, [and to the Msb, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlq","text_ar":"حلق"},{"kind":"text","text":", though it is there correctly and fully explained as meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"windpipe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqN","text_ar":"حَلْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but in the M it is explained [agreeably with general usage] as the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passage of the breath, and of coughing, from the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawof","text_ar":"جَوْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chest"},{"kind":"text","text":"];"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consisting of a series of successively-superimposed cartilages"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTobaAqu garaADiyfa","text_ar":"اَطْبَاقُ غَرَاضِيفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before which, in the exterior of the throat, is nothing but skin; having its lower extremity in the lungs, and its upper extremity at the root of the tongue: from it pass forth the breath and the wind and the saliva and the voice:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[see also another explanation voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqN","text_ar":"حَلْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", from Zj in his “ Khalk el-Insán, ” and the Msb:] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaAqimu","text_ar":"حَلَاقِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaAqiymu","text_ar":"حَلَاقِيمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) Accord. to some, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":"is augmentative: accord. to others, radical. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] they say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nazalonaA mivola Huloquwmi","text_ar":"نَزَلْنَا مِثْلَ حُلْقُومِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aEaAmapi","text_ar":"النَّعَامَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We alighted in a strait,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confined, place."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaAqiymu AlbilaAdi","text_ar":"حَلَاقِيمُ البِلَادِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The strait,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confined, parts of the country,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of countries:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the lateral,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extreme, parts thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["T","TA","Mgh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}